import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.scatter(data['US_Gross'], data['Worldwide_Gross'])
    plt.xlabel('US_Gross')
    plt.ylabel('Worldwide_Gross')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of US_Gross and Worldwide_Gross?', wrap=True)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['Production_Budget'], bins=20)
    plt.xlabel('Production Budget')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Production_Budget?')
    
    ax = plt.gca()
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['Running_Time_min'], bins='auto', edgecolor='black')

    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Running_Time_min?')

    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    mpaa_rating_counts = data['MPAA_Rating'].value_counts()
    mpaa_rating_counts.plot(kind='bar')
    plt.xlabel('MPAA Rating')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of MPAA_Rating?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
